Package proj3

Interface Summary
LoginInfo Contains information about database creation.
 

Class Summary
About This is a window for information about this program.
Create This is a module that allows someone to create and add questions to a test via a database connection.
DatabaseCreate This program creates table descriptions in the database.
DatabaseLoad This program populates tables in the database with some default data.
Main Gives the user the option of creating a new test, administering a test, or calling the DatabaseCreate and DatabaseLoad classes.
TestStudent This module tests the student by loading up questions from a database table.
